    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name ref="Alprandus">Aliprando</name></persName> filio
                            <persName>quondam <name ref="Marinus">Marini</name></persName> riceve da
                                <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs> rectorem adque custodem ecclesie <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/242" key="#Churches">Sancti Petri principis
                            apostolorum, sita foras civitate ista Lucense, que dicitur
                            Maiore</orgName>, per cartula livellario nomine (…), casa et res illa in
                            <placeName ref="#places/3302">loco et finibus Niciano, ubi dicitur
                            Casale</placeName>, quas quondam Mauricio massario ad manus suas abuit,
                        pertenentes ipsius ecclesie Sancti Petri; casa ipsa cum fundamento et
                        edeficio suo seu curte orto, terris, vineis, olivis, silvis, virgareis (…)
                        omnia quantum ubique ad ipsa casa est pertenentes et suprascripto <persName
                            key="#Agricultural_workers">quondam <name ref="Maurizo"
                            >Mauricio</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Agricultural_workers">massario</rs> exinde ad manus suas abuit, in
                        integrum mihi eas dedisti, tali ordinem ut admodum in mea vel
                                <persName><name ref="Ursus">Ursi</name></persName>, filio meo, vel
                        de suis heredes sint potestatem eas abendi, tenendi, inperandi, gubernandi,
                        laborare faciendi, meliorandi et nobis eas privatum nomine usufructuandi et
                        in ipsa casa homines ad residendum et abitandum mittere debeamus (…). Censo:
                        pro omni censum et iustitia (…) ad pars ipsius ecclesie Sancti Petri per
                        singulos annos, in mense martio, reddere debeamus, ad ipsa ecclesia Sancti
                        Petri, per nos aut per misso nostro, vobis vel ad misso vestro, argentum
                        denarios bonos, expendiviles, numero viginti quatuor et per omnem Cena
                        Domini (…) uno pario pulli cum ovas decem; et homines, illos qui in ipsa
                        casa abitantes fuerit, nos eum a mandato vestro venire faciamus hic
                            <placeName ref="#places/4" key="#Cities #Churches #Priests"
                            >Luca</placeName> legem et iustitiam faciendum tantum (…). Pena: spondeo
                        ego qui supra Aliprando, una cum suprascripto Urso, filio meo, vel suis
                        heredibus, conponere tibi (…) argentum soledos triginta (…). <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Teuderandus"
                            >Teuderandus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>. Actum Luca.
                        Sottoscrivono come testimoni: <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Ermipertus">Ermiperto</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Leo">Leo</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Notary"><name ref="Andreas">Andreas</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Ardemannus">Ardimanno</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Leo">Leo</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Scabini"><name ref="Benedictus"
                                >Benedicto</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Scabini">schabinus</rs>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
